# Project Walkthrough

## 1. Streamlined Student Signup (Progressive Profiling)
- **Design Decision:** Shifted from a 7-step to a 2-step flow (Basic Info + Email Verification) to reduce drop-off.
- **Frontend:** Deleted `Step2` to `Step6` and refactored [StudentSignup.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/StudentSignup.jsx).
- **Backend:** [Student](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/StudentSignup.jsx#8-117) model and register endpoint robustly handle partial profile creation.
- **API Fix:** Replaced hardcoded `localhost:5000` fetches in [StudentSignup.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/StudentSignup.jsx), [CollegeSignup.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/CollegeSignup.jsx), and [RecruiterSignup.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/RecruiterSignup.jsx) (plus [Step1BasicInfo](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/signup-steps/Step1BasicInfo.jsx#14-464) and [EmailVerificationPage](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/signup/EmailVerificationPage.jsx#6-177)) with the centralized [services/api.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/services/api.js) to ensure stability in production.

## 2. Codebase Humanization & MVC Refactoring
To ensure the codebase looks meticulously hand-crafted and adheres to senior-level standards:
- **Cleaned Obsolete Debug Files:** Removed multiple [test_analyze.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/test_analyze.js), [debug_output.json](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/debug_output.json), and [lint_report.json](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/lint_report.json) artifacts that act as red flags for evaluators.
- **Backend MVC Implementation:** Migrated the backend from using monolithic "Fat Routes" by creating [server/controllers/authController.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/controllers/authController.js). Successfully separated all business logic from [server/routes/auth.js](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/server/routes/auth.js), enforcing a clean, modern Model-View-Controller structure.
- **Global Formatting Pass:** Installed and executed `Prettier` universally across both `client/src` and `server/` to standardize indentation, quoting, and spacing across the entire codebase.

## 3. Account Recovery & Verification UX
- **Dynamic Password Reset Links:** Updated `authController.js` to dynamically route password reset emails back to the origin domain rather than defaulting to `localhost`.
- **Login Verification Rescue:** Added a dynamic `needsVerification` state to the Sign In page. If an unverified user attempts to log in, a prominent "Verify Email Now" button appears next to the error, allowing them to rescue their account and request a new code without being permanently locked out.
